                </p>
                <p class="case-study-heading2">High-level technologies:</p>
                <p class="case-study-text">C#, .NET7, Vanilla JS, Bootstrap, MySQL, Linux</p>
                <p class="case-study-heading2">Requirements-Based Features:</p>
                <ul class="case-study-text">
